title: 317: Squat vs. Deadlift, Leg Extensions, Overtraining & MORE
description: In this Quah Sal, Adam & Justin answer Pump Head questions about the importance of goals, if leg extensions really are a pointless exercise, what is overtraining and the symptoms of overtraining and what they would pick if they had to choose between the squat and deadlift.
